mpfit.py — Levenberg-Marquardt least-squares minimization
================================================================================
File:    circ/bootjtk/mpfit.py

This implementation traces back through three adaptations:

  1. MINPACK-1 (LMDIF.F) — original FORTRAN implementation
       More' J, Garbow B, Hillstrom K. "User Guide for MINPACK-1."
       Argonne National Laboratory Report ANL-80-74, 1980.

  2. IDL adaptation by Craig B. Markwardt
       Craig B. Markwardt, NASA/GSFC Code 662, Greenbelt, MD 20770
       craigm@lheamail.gsfc.nasa.gov

  3. Python adaptation by Mark Rivers
       Mark Rivers, University of Chicago / Argonne National Laboratory
       Building 434A, Argonne National Laboratory, 9700 South Cass Avenue,
       Argonne, IL 60439
       rivers@cars.uchicago.edu
